ote"><p><a href="https://www.unicreate.tokyo/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">尤尼创造有限公司</a></p><cite>官方网站</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp 经营代表“Mr.2（暂定）”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber 信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/liverary-management-uni-create-reports-on-termination-of-vtuber-mochizuki-himari-activity-and-her-crowdfunding-policy/">关于VTuber“望月Himari”活动结束情况和俱乐部粉丝政策的后图书馆管理Yuni Create报告首次</a>出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/liverary-management-uni-create-reports-on-termination-of-vtuber-mochizuki-himari-activity-and-her-crowdfunding-policy/feed/ 0 108464
