-has-seen-a-string-of-expulsions/">Nijisanji旗下的ANYCOLOR公司在经历了一系列的开除之后，还会继续推进新VTuber培养项目吗？</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“在许多人被驱逐之后，Nijisanji 运营的 ANYCOLOR 公司将继续推进新的 VTuber 培训项目” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/will-nijisanji-anycolor-continue-to-promote-a-new-vtubers-training-project-virtual-talent-academy-which-has-seen-a-string-of-expulsions/embed/#?secret=kuqqh0UNOc#?secret=d6YbdF2VXO" data-secret="d6YbdF2VXO" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>关于Nijisanji和ANYCOLOR，2023年6月（令和5年），一份关于Zaion LanZa的文件，该公司运营的VTuber团体NIJISANJI EN（新）取消了其<strong>人才</strong>合同（通称“Zion文件”）作品发布后，海外越来越多的人批评“ <em>Nijisanji（项目）和ANYCOLOR是黑公司</em>”。重新考虑环境的人才正在考虑和做出诸如毕业或转入其他机构或团体等选择。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="nmYdPxwtIf"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-foreign-vtuber-listeners-and-fans-are-increasingly-critical-of-nijisanji-and-anycolor-in-response-to-the-contents-of-zaion-lanza-document/">部分海外VTuber观众/粉丝收到“兰萨罪恶（Zaion LanZa）文件”，并加大对虹山寺和ANYCOLOR的批评力度</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“一些海外VTuber观众/粉丝收到“Zaion LanZa文件”并增加了对Nijisanji和ANYCOLOR的批评” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-foreign-vtuber-listeners-and-fans-are-increasingly-critical-of-nijisanji-and-anycolor-in-response-to-the-contents-of-zaion-lanza-document/embed/#?secret=BHlYX3tDNR#?secret=nmYdPxwtIf" data-secret="nmYdPxwtIf" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">虹山寺</a></p><cite>安尼色彩有限公司</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp 经营代表“Mr.2（暂定）”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber 信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="MWOa0g0SmN"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/nijisanji-vtuber-yuki-chihiro-and-azuchi-momo-to-graduate-as-of-january-31-2024/">NIJISANJI VTuber“Yuki Chihiro”和“Azuchi Momo”将于1月31日毕业</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“NIJISANJI VTuber“Yuki Chihiro”和“Azuchi Momo”将于 1 月 31 日毕业” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/nijisanji-vtuber-yuki-chihiro-and-azuchi-momo-to-graduate-as-of-january-31-2024/embed/#?secret=Z723xAC6nR#?secret=MWOa0g0SmN" data-secret="MWOa0g0SmN" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-vtuber-yuki-chihiro-and-azuchi-momo-to-graduate-as-of-january-31-2024/">Nijisanji 所属 VTuber“Chihiro Yuki”和“Momo Azuchi”将于 1 月 31 日毕业的帖子</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-vtuber-yuki-chihiro-and-azuchi-momo-to-graduate-as-of-january-31-2024/feed/ 0 108404
